Binary Search Tree'de arama, ekleme ve silme islemleri ortalama O(log n)'dir. Her adimda sol veya sag alt agaca gecilir, agacin yuksekligi log n kadardir.

Kod Ornegi:
```python
class BSTNode:
    def __init__(self, val):
        self.val = val
        self.left = None
        self.right = None

def search(root, target):
    if not root or root.val == target:
        return root
    if target < root.val:
        return search(root.left, target)
    return search(root.right, target)

# Dengeli BST'de O(log n)
```

Bagli listede (linked list) arama yapmak O(n)'dir. Her dugum sadece bir sonrakini bildigi icin istenen eleman bulunana kadar tum liste taranir.

Kod Ornegi:
```python
class Node:
    def __init__(self, val):
        self.val = val
        self.next = None

def find(head, target):
    curr = head
    while curr:
        if curr.val == target:
            return True
        curr = curr.next
    return False

# Linked list'te arama O(n)
```

Iki toplam probleminin cozumu O(n) hash map ile yapilabilir. Her eleman icin target - curr degeri hash'te aranir.

Kod Ornegi:
```python
def two_sum(nums, target):
    seen = {}
    for i, n in enumerate(nums):
        diff = target - n
        if diff in seen:
            return [seen[diff], i]
        seen[n] = i
    return []

print(two_sum([2, 7, 11, 15], 9))  # [0, 1], O(n)
```

Bubble sort, her elemani komsusuyla karsilastirarak yer degistirir. n eleman icin n kez, her seferinde n-1 karsilastirma = O(n^2). Basit ama yavas.

Kod Ornegi:
```python
def bubble_sort(arr):
    n = len(arr)
    for i in range(n):
        for j in range(0, n-i-1):
            if arr[j] > arr[j+1]:
                arr[j], arr[j+1] = arr[j+1], arr[j]
    return arr

print(bubble_sort([64, 34, 25, 12, 22, 11, 90]))
```

Selection sort, her adimda en kucuk elemani bulur ve dogru konuma yerlestirir. n * (n-1) / 2 karsilastirma yapar. Her durumda O(n^2)'dir.

Kod Ornegi:
```python
def selection_sort(arr):
    for i in range(len(arr)):
        min_idx = i
        for j in range(i+1, len(arr)):
            if arr[j] < arr[min_idx]:
                min_idx = j
        arr[i], arr[min_idx] = arr[min_idx], arr[i]
    return arr

print(selection_sort([29, 10, 14, 37, 13]))
```

Recursive binary search, call stack'te O(log n) bellek kullanir. Her recursive cagri stack'te bir yeni frame olusturur. n=1 milyon icin ~20 stack frame.

Kod Ornegi:
```python
def binary_search_recursive(arr, target, left, right):
    if left > right:
        return -1
    mid = (left + right) // 2
    if arr[mid] == target:
        return mid
    elif arr[mid] < target:
        return binary_search_recursive(arr, target, mid+1, right)
    else:
        return binary_search_recursive(arr, target, left, mid-1)

arr = [1, 3, 5, 7, 9]
print(binary_search_recursive(arr, 7, 0, len(arr)-1))  # O(log n) space
```

